beer.beer_description:
A well-balanced draught lager, this full-strength beer is more than a thirst quencher in South Australia; it's a symbol of camaraderie for its generations of ardent followers.

Exactly how strong is the allegiance of WED aficionados? Nearly one in six beers consumed in South Australia today is a West End beer and it has been on the beer scene for over 155 years.

INGREDIENTS

Malt: Pale Lager & Roasted Malt

Hops: Super Pride & Hop Extract

Yeast: Unique Australian Lager Yeast

Extras: Australian Cane Sugar
